    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nelumbra is a 2.5D roguelite time-survival game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>You embody the Light Bearer, a savior trying to survive throughout timeloops to discover about its own fate. Survive relentless celestial hordes and bosses, discover new characters, enhance your powers and shape your destiny with every loop. Will you break free or become part of the cycle forever?</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/f3ce44050c291b7ffb3b6a8fef634374.webp?t=1760120218\" width=560 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/94628d454984ef6e4aa8ee8d0db1a3d2.poster.avif?t=1760120218\" width=560 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/94628d454984ef6e4aa8ee8d0db1a3d2.webm?t=1760120218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/94628d454984ef6e4aa8ee8d0db1a3d2.mp4?t=1760120218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play with a fresh and unique dash mechanic. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Redirect and chain frenetic dashes to weave through hordes of enemies. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhance their power and effects as you progress, creating dynamic and powerful builds.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/81bfa2047b30ca1d5fd82cc3a2cf164b.webp?t=1760120218\" width=560 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/164c03b4cd594716f90cd2a8242c179c.poster.avif?t=1760120218\" width=560 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/164c03b4cd594716f90cd2a8242c179c.webm?t=1760120218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/164c03b4cd594716f90cd2a8242c179c.mp4?t=1760120218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Navigate your way through an obscure world where the light gradually fades around you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adapt your strategy find ways to recharge it throughout the game level.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feel the tension raise as shadows grow around you!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/a4c53d71a7073c70a126f598bfafd516.webp?t=1760120218\" width=560 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/bf218cd1a011f43345ef495d3f651d51.poster.avif?t=1760120218\" width=560 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/bf218cd1a011f43345ef495d3f651d51.webm?t=1760120218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/bf218cd1a011f43345ef495d3f651d51.mp4?t=1760120218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover 20 combinable celestial artefacts meant to shake your gameplay up.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhance your auto attacks, dashes... or create clones of yourself.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploit their strengths to survive your way out!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/5ae14c639d277df45dd25d8ed09ab82d.webp?t=1760120218\" width=560 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/e1b36c3c5c1cd12fd7d52eddf74c5878.poster.avif?t=1760120218\" width=560 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/e1b36c3c5c1cd12fd7d52eddf74c5878.webm?t=1760120218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/e1b36c3c5c1cd12fd7d52eddf74c5878.mp4?t=1760120218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/5ed0b96650f6388368bee5af1d829465.poster.avif?t=1760120218\" width=560 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/5ed0b96650f6388368bee5af1d829465.webm?t=1760120218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/5ed0b96650f6388368bee5af1d829465.mp4?t=1760120218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade your weapons between loops to create your preferred playstyle.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embrace and master your character's innate auto-attacks.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose between 5 characters and 8 hats to perfect your plan.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281380/extras/ca6c6bb7ec7181cd27dcf9ce922e316d.webp?t=1760120218\" width=300 height=55 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-Paced Runs:</strong> Complete intense and rewarding runs in under 15 minutes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Variety:</strong> Experiment with scaling builds using weapons, dashes and upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Characters:</strong> Unlock and discover characters with each their own playstyle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Items:</strong> Choose between 20 combinable celestial artefacts and build your own unique run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original Visuals and Audio:</strong> Dive into an immersive 2.5D celestial world with authentic graphics and audio, made by humans for humans</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accessibility Options:</strong> Tailor your own experience with different visual and controller accessibility settings</p></li></ul>",
